      show_infonote default drawing_language default
      comment "Precondition
Node must be opened yet and close need not to be in progress.
TX is not in progress (only one writer at a time).

Normal flow
1. request_space ioctl is called with count/size parameter
2. min(requested size, free space available in the ring buffer, some reliable constant -- to not allow one application transmit for a long time) is returned"
    end

