      comment "Precondition
Node must be opened yet and close need not to be in progress.
request_space was called by this application.

Normal flow
1. put_data ioctl is invoked with filled count
2. add to the HW.tx_head_ptr min(free space, requested count, the constant) -- application may cheat
3. successfully written count is returned"
    end

    usecase 128170 "close_node"
      //use case diagram settings
      package_name_in_tab default show_context default auto_label_position default draw_all_relations default shadow default
