      show_infonote default drawing_language default
      comment "Precondition
Hardware was started and expected to run (i.e. refcount > 0)

Normal flow
1. interrupt (timeout or ring buffer pointer reached) is raised -- data ready in the ring buffer
2. wake applications, which are waiting for this data up

Alternative flow
* missed interrupt -- set up timer (watchdog) to cope with this"
    end

